      "raw": "At tau=0 (homogeneous SU(3)), d_s = 8 at ALL scales (high degeneracies enforce this).",
      "type": "code",
      "context": "For a d-dimensional Riemannian manifold, Weyl's law gives d_s -> d as sigma -> 0.",
      "session": "19a",
      "source_file": "tier0-computation\\s19a_spectral_dimension.py",
      "line": 10,
      "existing_latex": "",
      "audit_status": "none",
